3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing an intelligent system to learn balanced performance for different races. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the fairness and accuracy of face recognition systems, which can have implications for security and privacy. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image and video data.
